title: Huge 2bd/2.5ba Townhouse with 2 Car Attached Garage! Avail now!
posting_body: ['Available Now!', 'Please email leasing with inquiries and showing requests.', 'Spacious, high-end townhouse featuring:', '- Hardwood Floors', '- High Ceilings', "- Custom 42'' cabinets", '- 2 car attached garage', '- Granite Counters and Island', '- Premium lighting package', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Kohler fixtures', '- Luxury master bath with double vanity sink, Jacuzzi tub, shower with body sprays', '- Private patio', '- Side-by-side laundry', '- Large bedrooms', '- Plenty of closet space', '- About 1 mile from Metra station', '- Small pet friendly (cats & dogs up to 40lbs, pet fee, breed restrictions)', "- Close to vibrant downtown LaGrange with Metra Station, many appealing restaurants (Francesca's Bellezza, Prasino, etc.), coffee shops (Starbucks), Forever Yogurt, stylish boutiques, and much much more!", 'Images are of exact or very similar unit on site.', 'Terms:', '$400 Nonrefundable Move-In Fee', 'No Security Deposit', 'General Credit and Income Requirements:', '- 650+ credit score', '- Gross monthly income should be at lease 3x the rent', '(There are some exceptions to these requirements, such as being a student and having a cosigner)', "Don't miss this!", 'Meltzer Real Estate LLC', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
